---
title: Cal Smart Beef 'Un-Fried' Rice with Green Veggies
description: We've lightened up fried rice by not frying it at all! Instead, we're combining ground beef, green beans and peas, a wild rice medley and savoury ginger sauce to create a wholesome jumble.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/riz-fritau-boeuf-441e7767.jpg
